	<entry>
		<title>Podcast Suite, Version 1.1 Stable</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://jlleblanc.com/articles/41-podcast-suite-version-11-stable"/>
		<published>2006-09-06T21:41:49Z</published>
		<updated>2006-09-06T21:41:49Z</updated>
		<id>http://jlleblanc.com/articles/41-podcast-suite-version-11-stable</id>
		<summary type="html">&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Podcast Suite version 1.1 stable is now available for download: &lt;a href=&quot;http://jlleblanc.com/com_podcast_v1.1.zip&quot;&gt;component&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;http://jlleblanc.com/mod_podcast_v.1.1.zip&quot;&gt;module&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;http://jlleblanc.com/bot_podcast_v1.1.zip&quot;&gt;plugin&lt;/a&gt;. This is mainly a bug fix release, with the following issues resolved:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Added support for &amp;lt;itunes:author&amp;gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fixed the iTunes category format&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fixed player autostart issues in IE&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fixed the issue where RSS feeds were downloading instead of displaying in the browser&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Enclosures can now appear in both the introtext and fulltext&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Off-site links now work properly&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fixed so that filenames with parenthesis are properly handled &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;The following features were also added:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;The module can now display pcast:// links for one-click subscriptions, as well as display an additional link to the actual feed&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Quicktime is now supported for AAC playback&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Category pre-selects have been added for iTunes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Feeds for separate Joomla categories are now available.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;Uninstall the old versions of all three, then reinstall the new copies.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;

Translations:&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.nik-o-mat.de/joomlafan/joomla-software/podcastsuite-1.1-stable---deutsch.html&quot;&gt;German&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;


webman911 has graciously written a &lt;a href=&quot;http://forum.joomla.org/index.php/topic,138839.0.html&quot;&gt;step-by-step tutorial&lt;/a&gt; for using the podcasting suite!</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Podcast Suite version 1.1 stable is now available for download: &lt;a href=&quot;http://jlleblanc.com/com_podcast_v1.1.zip&quot;&gt;component&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;http://jlleblanc.com/mod_podcast_v.1.1.zip&quot;&gt;module&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;http://jlleblanc.com/bot_podcast_v1.1.zip&quot;&gt;plugin&lt;/a&gt;. This is mainly a bug fix release, with the following issues resolved:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Added support for &amp;lt;itunes:author&amp;gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fixed the iTunes category format&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fixed player autostart issues in IE&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fixed the issue where RSS feeds were downloading instead of displaying in the browser&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Enclosures can now appear in both the introtext and fulltext&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Off-site links now work properly&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fixed so that filenames with parenthesis are properly handled &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;The following features were also added:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;The module can now display pcast:// links for one-click subscriptions, as well as display an additional link to the actual feed&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Quicktime is now supported for AAC playback&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Category pre-selects have been added for iTunes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Feeds for separate Joomla categories are now available.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;Uninstall the old versions of all three, then reinstall the new copies.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;

