		<title>Updated mp3 player</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://jlleblanc.com/articles/30-updated-mp3-player"/>
		<published>2005-06-15T10:33:13Z</published>
		<updated>2005-06-15T10:33:13Z</updated>
		<id>http://jlleblanc.com/articles/30-updated-mp3-player</id>
		<summary type="html">
An updated copy of the mp3 player has been released. There is now a &lt;a href=&quot;http://jlleblanc.com/mod_mp3player1_1.zip&quot;&gt;module&lt;/a&gt; as well as a &lt;a href=&quot;http://jlleblanc.com/mp3player1_2.zip&quot;&gt;component&lt;/a&gt;. You must have the component installed to use the module.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The mp3 player is designed to pull mp3 files from the root of your Joomla installation. To use subdirectories, simply add them before the filename (example: images/stories/mymp3song.mp3 instead of just mymp3song.mp3).&lt;br /&gt;
</summary>
		<content type="html">
An updated copy of the mp3 player has been released. There is now a &lt;a href=&quot;http://jlleblanc.com/mod_mp3player1_1.zip&quot;&gt;module&lt;/a&gt; as well as a &lt;a href=&quot;http://jlleblanc.com/mp3player1_2.zip&quot;&gt;component&lt;/a&gt;. You must have the component installed to use the module.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The mp3 player is designed to pull mp3 files from the root of your Joomla installation. To use subdirectories, simply add them before the filename (example: images/stories/mymp3song.mp3 instead of just mymp3song.mp3).&lt;br /&gt;
</content>
